snippet: Vasek Pospisil of Canada was the only seed not to reach the Chennai Open second round when he lost to Aljaz Bedene of Britain 7-5, 7-6 (6) on Tuesday....
lead_paragraph: Vasek Pospisil of Canada was the only seed not to reach the Chennai Open second round when he lost to Aljaz Bedene of Britain 7-5, 7-6 (6) on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Pospisil Knocked Out in Chennai Open 1st Round by Bedene
headline.main: Pospisil Knocked Out in Chennai Open 1st Round by Bedene
